<p><a name="References" id="References"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Vertical_integration&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11" title="Edit section: References">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">References</span></h2>
<div class="references-small">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-0"><b><a href="#cite_ref-0" title="">^</a></b> Folsom, Burton <i>The Myth of the Robber Barons</i> 5th edition. 2007. pg 65 "only we can develop <i>ability</i> and hold it in our service. Every year should be marked by the promotion of one or more of our young men."</li>
